# Copy to `.npmrc` in any app that depends on @4kgraphics/engine (Atelier3D, the
# storefront build, etc.). Maps the @4kgraphics scope to GitHub Packages and
# reads the auth token from the NODE_AUTH_TOKEN env var (a GitHub PAT with the
# read:packages scope). Commit this file — it holds no secret, only the
# placeholder. See docs/PUBLISHING.md.
#
# NOTE: this monorepo does NOT use this file — its workspaces resolve the engine
# locally. It's a template for OTHER repos.
@4kgraphics:registry=https://npm.pkg.github.com
//npm.pkg.github.com/:_authToken=${NODE_AUTH_TOKEN}
